{"tid":1255752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部: 搞亂香港對美國沒好處，促請美方收回干的黑手","createTime":"2019-06-24T15:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:17:41.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7026d37bdd097f233bd2be123f7a33661cde90ac","tid":1255752,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"外交部促美國國會議員勿通過涉港法案<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台】美國跨黨派國會議員重推《香港人權和民主法案》，在北京，外交部回應指，搞亂香港對美國沒好處，促請美方收回企圖干預香港事務的黑手。<br />\n<br />\n由美國民主黨和共和黨議員重推，並獲眾議院議長佩洛西支持的《香港人權和民主法案》，要求國務院每年「認證」香港自治，確保符合《香港政策法》的特別待遇標準，即擁有獨立關稅區地位，對於任何遏制香港基本自由的人，美國總統有權凍結他們在美國的資產，並拒絕發出簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=351757&amp;fbclid=IwAR155zHyx9HF48S6vlWFVyAA7nw7K6cMMZvKKEI8jfZFiK5sroayPRf7tcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351757%26fbclid%3DIwAR155zHyx9HF48S6vlWFVyAA7nw7K6cMMZvKKEI8jfZFiK5sroayPRf7tcg&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=4e3c86d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351757%26fbclid%3DIwAR155zHyx9HF48S6vlWFVyAA7nw7K6cMMZvKKEI8jfZFiK5sroayPRf7tcg&h=179c1855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=351757&amp;fbclid=IwAR155zHyx9HF48S6vlWFVyAA7nw7K6cMMZvKKEI8jfZFiK5sroayPRf7tcg</a>"},{"pid":"542ea3895fdd1d93e9dc62c63099d6ed94ccbae8","tid":1255752,"uid":267953,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"又干涉美國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b0af0a1d15d4ffc29cc596286f73590ec8f3cb","tid":1255752,"uid":93383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"點解共匪硬係認為一定係美國搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：真蠢"},{"pid":"67ffb1efb3fea64789b6ac995c696f3b5f88d297","tid":125575